{"comments":"Lookup Tables for Color Grading.\n\n**PROFESSIONAL COLOR GRADING INFRASTRUCTURE:**\nLUTs (Look-Up Tables) are the backbone of professional color workflows.\nThey map input colors to output colors, enabling:\n- Camera log to display transforms\n- Creative color grading looks\n- Color space conversions\n- HDR tonemapping\n\n**LUT Types:**\n- `LUT1D` - Per-channel curves (1024-65536 entries per channel)\n- `LUT3D` - Full color cube (17x17x17 to 65x65x65 entries)\n\n**Industry Formats:**\n- .cube (Adobe/Blackmagic - most common)\n- .3dl (Lustre)\n- .look (ACES)\n- .clf (Common LUT Format - ACES standard)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LUT"],"LUT1D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[187,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LUT.purs","start":[187,1]},"title":"eqLUT1D"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LUT"],"LUT1D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[191,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LUT.purs","start":[189,1]},"title":"showLUT1D"}],"comments":"1D Lookup Table (per-channel curves)\n\nA 1D LUT applies the same curve to each RGB channel independently.\nUsed for gamma curves, log-to-linear, contrast adjustments.\n\nEach entry is a Number in 0.0-1.0 range representing the output\nvalue for that input index.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[185,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LUT.purs","start":[180,1]},"title":"LUT1D"},{"children":